doc.previous: Until 1917 Nantucket was served by the narrow gauge Nantucket Railroad  Nantucket Regional Transit Authority NRTA operates seasonal island wide shuttle buses to many destinations including Surfside Beach Siasconset and the airport
doc.after: Nantucket waters were the site of several noted transportation disasters  The following Nantucket places are listed on the National Register of Historic Places 40
